patthana17.29:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ vipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho navipāko dhammo
patthana17.29:1.1_1: uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… aññamaññe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana17.29:2.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
patthana17.29:3.1_1: nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā tīṇi …pe… avigate tīṇi.
